description:
It comes every time to my balcony to sip nectar in a cup (tea time).  

This animation is based on a picture I took some months ago, and how it is made :

1) Read the picture file converting it into three matrices - red, blue and green ; 
3) Slice every matrix in 4 lines by 4 columns sub matrices and assign a sequence accordingly ;
4) Mix everything randomly ;
5) Apply a cocktail shaker algorithm to sort everything out.

For this animation I used only the red and blue channel to give it a reddish tint.

All process was done in Python 3 using Matplolib, Numpy, Pillow and Random libraries.
